4121
03:24:30.585 --> 03:24:34.045
Um, so when you work in natural hazards,

4122
03:24:34.385 --> 03:24:37.325
people often ask us, what's the single biggest thing

4123
03:24:37.715 --> 03:24:39.765
that could reduce the impact of disasters?

4124
03:24:40.625 --> 03:24:42.325
And I think most of us agree

4125
03:24:42.715 --> 03:24:46.045
that it's not better emergency response capability.

4126
03:24:46.105 --> 03:24:48.725
Mm-hmm. It's not better hazard models.

4127
03:24:49.275 --> 03:24:51.405
It's not even better engineering.

4128
03:24:52.515 --> 03:24:56.245
It's making sure our planning system consistently steers

4129
03:24:56.245 --> 03:24:59.285
development away from the very highest risk places

4130
03:24:59.825 --> 03:25:00.845
in the first place.

4131
03:25:03.295 --> 03:25:05.785
Most of the losses New Zealand experiences from natural

4132
03:25:05.815 --> 03:25:08.185
hazards are not caused by the hazard itself.

4133
03:25:09.215 --> 03:25:12.985
They're caused by the exposure we create over time

4134
03:25:13.375 --> 03:25:15.985
through the decisions we make on where we build

4135
03:25:16.085 --> 03:25:19.545
and how we build, how our land is used,

4136
03:25:20.245 --> 03:25:21.705
how intensively we build,

4137
03:25:22.325 --> 03:25:24.585
and whether risk is recognized early enough

4138
03:25:24.585 --> 03:25:25.825
to shape good decisions.

4139
03:25:27.515 --> 03:25:29.625
Those decisions accumulate over decades

4140
03:25:30.735 --> 03:25:32.825
when they recognize natural hazard risk.

4141
03:25:33.005 --> 03:25:36.635
The impacts of events can be manageable when they don't.

4142
03:25:37.175 --> 03:25:39.995
The costs are measured in lives, lost houses,

4143
03:25:40.105 --> 03:25:42.195
damaged disrupted communities,

4144
03:25:42.455 --> 03:25:44.315
and very large recovery bills.

4145
03:25:46.075 --> 03:25:49.085
Through the claims we receive under the Natural Hazards

4146
03:25:49.085 --> 03:25:50.085
Insurance Scheme.

4147
03:25:50.665 --> 03:25:51.885
We see the consequences

4148
03:25:51.985 --> 03:25:53.645
of those decisions very clearly

4149
03:25:53.945 --> 03:25:55.125
in the claims that we receive.

4150
03:25:56.465 --> 03:25:59.635
Many of the losses we deal with arise from development

4151
03:25:59.635 --> 03:26:02.395
that has occurred in places where the risk is already known.

4152
03:26:04.885 --> 03:26:06.775
That is why land use planning is one

4153
03:26:06.775 --> 03:26:08.895
of the most powerful risk reduction tools

4154
03:26:08.895 --> 03:26:10.135
available to New Zealand.

4155
03:26:11.935 --> 03:26:14.465
Natural hazard losses are not just insurance losses.

4156
03:26:14.855 --> 03:26:17.985
They fall across the system on households,

4157
03:26:18.285 --> 03:26:19.385
on local government,

4158
03:26:19.805 --> 03:26:22.905
on infrastructure providers, and on the crown.

4159
03:26:23.895 --> 03:26:25.985
When insurance cover narrows

4160
03:26:26.045 --> 03:26:29.665
or declines even more of tho those costs shift

4161
03:26:29.665 --> 03:26:30.865
to household and government.

4162
03:26:31.605 --> 03:26:33.705
And we're seeing that, um, quite recently,

4163
03:26:35.635 --> 03:26:38.235
planning decisions therefore shape not only the physical

4164
03:26:38.235 --> 03:26:41.195
risk, but long-term fiscal exposure as well.

4165
03:26:42.785 --> 03:26:45.445
For that reason, these bills are important.

4166
03:26:46.395 --> 03:26:49.125
They're not just about improving planning processes.

4167
03:26:49.635 --> 03:26:52.165
They're about whether New Zealand's planning framework

4168
03:26:52.165 --> 03:26:53.725
consistently recognizes

4169
03:26:53.785 --> 03:26:57.805
and manages natural hazard risk at its least costly

4170
03:26:57.805 --> 03:26:58.845
intervention point.

4171
03:27:00.215 --> 03:27:02.705
Once development is in place, the choices available

4172
03:27:02.805 --> 03:27:05.945
to us are much narrower and far more costly.

4173
03:27:08.295 --> 03:27:10.835
In our view, the draft legislation represents a

4174
03:27:10.835 --> 03:27:11.875
significant step forward.

4175
03:27:13.515 --> 03:27:16.895
