4176
03:27:16.895 --> 03:27:17.975
risk-based planning

4177
03:27:18.475 --> 03:27:20.015
and the clearer expectation

4178
03:27:20.015 --> 03:27:21.735
that natural hazard risk must be

4179
03:27:21.935 --> 03:27:23.055
considered in decision making.

4180
03:27:24.795 --> 03:27:26.135
The test will be in how it's

4181
03:27:26.135 --> 03:27:27.695
implemented and operationalized.

4182
03:27:28.465 --> 03:27:29.975
There are significant opportunities,

4183
03:27:30.595 --> 03:27:33.855
but we also need to guard against inconsistent practice.

4184
03:27:35.845 --> 03:27:38.185
