otherwise prevent risk reduction.

4202
03:28:25.195 --> 03:28:26.305
Third, we suggest

4203
03:28:26.305 --> 03:28:28.865
that the legislation provide a nationally consistent

4204
03:28:28.865 --> 03:28:30.865
mechanism to address situations

4205
03:28:31.155 --> 03:28:34.545
where serious natural hazard risk to life is identified

4206
03:28:35.525 --> 03:28:38.905
